Telkom has served unions with section 189 notices. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Communications Workers Union (CWU) says it will oppose planned retrenchments at Telkom. Telkom has served unions with section 189 notices. READ: Cell C drops Telkom At least 3,000 Telkom employees will be affected, a third of its workforce. "Out of respect for our employees, we will share information once we have engaged further with our employees and unions," company spokesperson Mooketsi Mocumi said in a WhatsApp response to questions.